e, double, four in hand. I've driven a sort of stage coach. Yes. Well there's only - a quarter lock - on a stagecoach.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12803377 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid342552\charrsid16715884 What's a quarter lock?
