Well - a full lock goes right round. But a quarter is only a quarter. If you turn it too sharp - it'll toss over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12803377 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid342552\charrsid16715884 This is some sort of wheel that you steer with?
