When I came home from school - I used to either get a set of harness to clean - or wash horses legs. Before I got me tea. Well, it was no good grumbling, had it to to do.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12803377 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid342552\charrsid16715884 You weren't afraid of horses?
