\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6759957 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid342552\charrsid16715884 
Well - in winter we used to get cord - what we called corduroys. And them was - {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Stanley{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}'s, underneath the Arches in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
