Well - we got - how much did we get, public assistance? Thirty-one shilling weren't it? Thirty-one shilling. Twenty-eight. For five of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12803377 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid342552\charrsid16715884 How did they treat you when you went for it?
