hey asked for your background, always questioned you on your background and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12803377 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid342552\charrsid16715884 How did you feel about having to go for it, did it upset you?
